service-1", "currencyservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-04": ["paymentservice-2", "frontend-0", "currencyservice-0", "checkoutservice-1", "cartservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-05": ["productcatalogservice-1", "paymentservice-1", "cartservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-06": ["frontend-1", "emailservice-2", "currencyservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-07": ["shippingservice-1", "emailservice-0", "adservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["redis-cart-0", "recommendationservice-0", "adservice-2", "checkoutservice-0", "frontend-2", "paymentservice-0", "productcatalogservice-0"]}, "matched_anomaly": "A fault occurred from 2025-06-27T16:10:01Z to 2025-06-27T16:35:01Z. Please identify the root cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-27 16:10:01+00:00 to 2025-06-27 16:35:01+00:00"}, "metric_data_collected": true, "node_pod_mapping": {"aiops-k8s-01": ["emailservice-1", "recommendationservice-2", "shippingservice-0", "productcatalogservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-02": [], "aiops-k8s-03": ["cartservice-1", "adservice-0", "shippingservice-2", "checkoutservice-2", "recommendationservice-1", "currencyservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-04": ["paymentservice-2", "frontend-0", "currencyservice-0", "checkoutservice-1", "cartservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-05": ["productcatalogservice-1", "paymentservice-1", "cartservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-06": ["frontend-1", "emailservice-2", "currencyservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-07": ["shippingservice-1", "emailservice-0", "adservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["redis-cart-0", "recommendationservice-0", "adservice-2", "checkoutservice-0", "frontend-2", "paymentservice-0", "productcatalogservice-0"]}, "log_analysis_findings": "```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [],\n  \"hypotheses\": []\n}\n```", "trace_analysis_findings": "通过分析提供的异常数据，我找到了一些显著的调用链异常，以下是我的发现。\n\n### 分析结果\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"latency_spike\",\n    \"frontend->checkoutservice\",\n    \"frontend->currencyservice\",\n    \"frontend->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"cartservice->redis\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CurrencyService\",\n      \"reason\": \"延迟显著上升 ('frontend->currencyservice')\",\n      \"evidence\": {\n        \"operation_name\": [\n          \"hipstershop.CurrencyService/GetSupportedCurrencies\",\n          \"hipstershop.CurrencyService/Convert\"\n        ],\n        \"normal_avg_duration\": [2864.12, 2325.68],\n        \"anomaly_avg_duration\": [82264.36, 93422.63]\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CheckoutService\",\n      \"reason\": \"延迟显著上升 ('frontend->checkoutservice')\",\n      \"evidence\": {\n        \"operation_name\": \"hipstershop.CheckoutService/PlaceOrder\",\n        \"normal_avg_duration\": 148672.42,\n        \"anomaly_avg_duration\": 402779.29\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"Redis (CartService)\",\n      \"reason\": \"异常 Redis 操作 ('cartservice->redis')\",\n      \"evidence\": {\n        \"operation_name\": \"HMSET\",\n        \"normal_avg_duration\": 1361.25,\n        \"anomaly_avg_duration\": 14828.15\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"ProductCatalogService\",\n      \"reason\": \"部分查询显著缓慢 ('frontend->productcatalogservice')\",\n      \"evidence\": {\n        \"operation_name\": [\n          \"hipstershop.ProductCatalogService/ListProducts\",\n          \"hipstershop.ProductCatalogService/GetProduct\"\n        ],\n        \"normal_avg_duration\": [1968.26, 8592.95],\n        \"anomaly_avg_duration\": [3979.69, 10614.37]\n      }\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### 主要问题\n1. **CurrencyService 延迟**：`frontend->currencyservice` 的调用链有显著的延迟，延迟倍数达到约 20-40 倍。\n2. **CheckoutService 延迟**：`frontend->checkoutservice` 的延迟倍数达到近 2-3 倍，影响订单下单的流程。\n3. **Redis 操作异常**：`cartservice->redis` 的异常操作延迟显著增加，可能存在 Redis 连接问题。\n4. **ProductCatalogService 响应变慢**：部分查询，例如 ListProducts 或 GetProduct 的时间翻倍。\n\n### 下一步\n进一步定位根因：\n- 检查 CurrencyService 和 CheckoutService 的资源压力或后端服务可用性。\n- 确认 Redis 配置和缓存策略是否异常。\n- 产品目录的数据库查询需要优化或分析流量热点是否存在问题。\n\n若有后续问题，请随时提问！", "metric_analysis_findings": "### 异常指标分析报告\n\n**1. 检测到的异常指标**\n从故障期间的 Trace 和监控数据中，识别出以下显著异常指标：\n\n- `error_ratio`: 在 `adservice` 和 `client_error_ratio` 中变化显著，但正常和故障期间的中位数没有改变，错误比例在故障期间的 p99 值显著上升。\n- `pod_cpu_usage`: 在多个 Pod 上的 CPU 使用率从 0% 到 40% 显著增加。\n- `rrt_max` 和 `rrt`: `currencyservice` 和 `frontend` 服务的响应时间显著增加，最大值和平均值在故障期间剧烈变化。\n- `pod_processes`: `currencyservice` 中的进程数量显著上升。\n\n**2. 关键异常组件与原因**\n\n- **Component**: `aiops-k8s-08`\n  - **Reason**: `error_ratio` 和 `client_error_ratio` 指标变化表明 `adservice` 服务的性能下降。而 `pod_cpu_usage` 的显著增加暗示 `currencyservice` 使用的计算资源高于正常水平，导致响应时间（`rrt_max` 和 `rrt`）严重异常。\n  - **Evidence**: \n    - `error_ratio` p99 在 adservice 中由 0.0 上升到 4.65。\n    - `pod_cpu_usage` 的中位数在 currencyservice 从 0.0 增加到 0.4。\n    - `rrt_max` 在 currencyservice 中由 6277.5 增加到 299647.0。\n\n**3. `detected_metric_keys`**\n\n```json\n{\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"client_error_ratio\",\n    \"pod_cpu_usage\",\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"rrt\",\n    \"pod_processes\"\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**4. 综合评估与假设**\n\n- **推测假设**：\n  - `aiops-k8s-08` 作为异常节点，可能已导致 Pod（如 `currencyservice-*` 和 `frontend-*`）的资源竞争或性能下降。\n  - `adservice` 的服务性能异常可能与节点资源使用高峰相关联。\n  - 进一步调查节点上的资源缓存、负载分配策略可能有助于理解 CPU 使用率增加的根本原因。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"client_error_ratio\",\n    \"pod_cpu_usage\",\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"rrt\",\n    \"pod_processes\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-08\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio and client_error_ratio exhaustion causing pod degradation\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio p99 increased in adservice from 0.0 to 4.65; pod_cpu_usage median increased in currencyservice from 0.0 to 0.4; rrt_max increased in currencyservice from 6277.5 to 299647.0\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n请在执行更具体的系统资源监控和负载测试以确认因素后，采取相应的补救措施。"}
